    public abstract class ChildWindow
extends javax.swing.JInternalFrame
implements java.awt.event.FocusListener
    The base class for all RNAstructure GUI dialogs and windows. These are "children" of the JDesktopPane. AppMainFrame-->JDesktopPane-->[ChildWindow(s)...]
